divs: Sighting DetailsMy father called me December 16, 2012 excited saying there was this UFO looking thing on his front gate security camera when he reviewed the memory card. The front gate security camera is a motion activated camera for taking pictures of deer in the woods for hunting. These are the photo's.. picture one is before the UFO.. picture two is the UFO pix, picture three is after.. That's pretty much it.. I just wish i would have been there and seen it and had a video camera and a full tank of gas.
Summary: disc object found on front gate security camera at farm
